snippet.title: Gender, Amber Heard and aging women, with Justin from Human Warnings channel.
snippet.description:
✘ A Toronto/Buenos Aires overseas, Sunday chat on gender, Amber Heard, aging women, and whether we need to try and keep on improving and changing things--or whether is it better to just accept them the way they are (and are they?)... the Machiavellian way. 

 Link to Human Warnings' video 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QzzAgSq6CW0 

#amberheard #metoo #feminism #podcast

March 1st, 2020
